=Miss The Dragon=

17
00:01:37,281 --> 00:01:39,953
=Episod 16=

18
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:42,040
(Astaka Luo Feng)

19
00:01:53,919 --> 00:01:55,680
Adakah saya

20
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,839
terlalu garang tadi?

21
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,639
Bagaimanapun, dia tetap Tuan Xue.

22
00:01:59,839 --> 00:02:02,000
Malah, dia beri saya banyak perhiasan

23
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,599
supaya saya jadi cantik.

24
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:09,320
Adakah dia sangat
ambil berat terhadap saya?

25
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,919
Semua salah awak.

26
00:02:13,119 --> 00:02:15,399
Awak menyebabkan saya
juga jadi menyampah.

27
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,479
Tuan Xue mungkin...

28
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,839
Takkan pedulikan saya lagi.

29
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:35,520
(Jika gadis dewa turunkan hujan, dia
akan dapat kurniaan dan menjadi gundik)

30
00:02:35,839 --> 00:02:36,600
Kamu rasa,

31
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,880
betulkah ada gadis dewa
yang boleh tolong kita?

32
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,000
Dengar khabar,

33
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,000
Mahaguru Wang sangat hebat.

34
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,800
Dia guna tali ikat dewa
dan lelabu Ba Bao

35
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,240
untuk hapuskan syaitan

36
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,160
yang bernama Qingqing itu.

37
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,520
Begini hebat?

38
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:50,320
Kalau Qingqing ialah syaitan,

39
00:02:50,485 --> 00:02:52,446
mungkinkah Ayu yang selalu bersama dia

40
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,240
ialah syaitan juga?

41
00:02:54,839 --> 00:02:55,839
Merepek!

42
00:02:56,119 --> 00:02:57,479
Saya tak merepek!

43
00:02:57,679 --> 00:02:58,720
Dia memang syaitan!

44
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:00,039
Jika muncul syaitan di pekan ini,

45
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,600
bagaimana kita nak
hidup dengan aman kelak?

46
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,520
Betul tak?

47
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,479
Betul itu.

48
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,520
Ayu bukan syaitan!

49
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:06,639
Kalau kata-kata awak betul,

50
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,160
awak membesar bersama dia,

51
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,440
maksudnya awak juga syaitan?

52
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,919
Saya berbeza dengan Ayu!

53
00:03:11,119 --> 00:03:12,600
Dia menyebabkan mak dia
mati semasa dilahirkan.

54
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,119
Dia juga menyebabkan Abang Zhiyong mati.

55
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,839
Kebakaran itu menyebabkan Abang Zhiyong

56
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,199
dibakar dengan teruk sekali.

57
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,479
Namun, Ayu selamat saja.

58
00:03:19,679 --> 00:03:21,479
Dia ialah apa kalau bukan syaitan?

59
00:03:22,279 --> 00:03:24,399
-Betul!
-Dia ialah syaitan!

60
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:26,360
Anak saya bukan syaitan!

61
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,279
Dia...

62
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:29,919
Dia ialah apa?

63
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:30,839
-Dia...
-Cakaplah.

64
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,199
Dia ialah gadis dewa!

65
00:03:33,679 --> 00:03:34,759
Ia tertulis pada notis diraja ini.

66
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,800
(Gadis dewa di selatan)
Gadis dewa turun di kawasan tenggara.

67
00:03:37,119 --> 00:03:40,559
Ayu ialah gadis dewa itu!

68
00:03:40,839 --> 00:03:42,399
Siapa ialah gadis dewa?

69
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:44,679
Tolong beri laluan!

70
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:49,320
Semua beri laluan kepada tuan!

71
00:03:49,348 --> 00:03:51,046
(Senyap)

72
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:58,600
Siapa sebut tentang gadis dewa tadi?

73
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,000
Dia.

74
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,119
Dia kata anaknya ialah gadis dewa.

75
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,320
Tuan.

76
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,360
Tolong dengar penjelasan hamba.

77
00:04:06,559 --> 00:04:08,800
Saya cakap-cakap saja.

78
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,240
Berani awak main-main
dengan notis diraja!

79
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,720
Pengawal, tangkap dia!

80
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,639
Ya, tuan!

81
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,359
Ini cuma salah faham, tuan!

82
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,760
-Tuan.
-Tunggu sebentar!

83
00:04:18,359 --> 00:04:19,480
Ayu dah datang.

84
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,399
Ayah.

85
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,440
Kenapa tangkap ayah saya?

86
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,679
Siapa awak?

87
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:24,760
-Saya...
-Tuan!

88
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,399
Dia anak perempuan pesalah ini!

89
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:28,119
Dia yang menyamar sebagai gadis dewa.

90
00:04:28,559 --> 00:04:29,480
Hal ini tiada kaitan dengan dia!

91
00:04:29,679 --> 00:04:30,679
Saya yang cakap begitu,

92
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:32,480
jadi tangkaplah saya seorang saja.

93
00:04:33,359 --> 00:04:33,959
Bawa dia pergi.

94
00:04:34,119 --> 00:04:34,880
Tunggu!

95
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,200
Betul cakap ayah saya.

96
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:39,040
Saya ialah gadis dewa
yang baginda cari.

97
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:49,119
Awak ialah gadis dewa?

98
00:04:49,559 --> 00:04:50,359
Ya.

99
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,880
Bukankah notis ini tertulis,

100
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:54,399
dunia dilanda kemarau teruk, jadi
minta gadis dewa untuk turunkan hujan?

101
00:04:54,799 --> 00:04:55,720
Saya boleh turunkan hujan.

102
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:05,000
Bagaimana awak nak turunkan hujan?

103
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:09,480
Lepaskan ayah saya dahulu.

104
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,600
Baik. Lepaskan dia.

105
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,359
Ayu.

106
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,000
Ayah, jangan risau.

107
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:20,600
Tuan, sediakan altar.

108
00:05:21,119 --> 00:05:22,920
Saya buat sihir untuk turunkan hujan.

109
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:26,399
Pergi sediakan altar.

110
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,359
Ya.

111
00:05:29,799 --> 00:05:31,000
Turunkan hujan?

112
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:33,720
Penipuan Ayu agak besar.

113
00:05:34,239 --> 00:05:36,799
Biarpun awak Raja Naga
dan boleh turunkan sedikit hujan,

114
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,600
tak mungkin awak

115
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:40,239
boleh turunkan hujan
di Pekan Yuchi yang besar ini.

116
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,040
Saya pergi pinjam Jampi Seru Hujan

117
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,359
dari Altar Lei Ze.

118
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,440
Pinjam kononnya.

119
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,600
Awak nak merampasnya!

120
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,839
Kamu tak dibenarkan masuk.

121
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,040
Saya nak lukis mantera.

122
00:06:03,239 --> 00:06:04,720
Ia takkan berfungsi jika dikacau.

123
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,799
Kami akan tunggu di sini.

124
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:09,200
Ayuh.

125
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:19,119
Ayah telah menyusahkan awak.

126
00:06:19,679 --> 00:06:21,079
Kenapa ayah nak bercakap besar?

127
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:23,200
Ayah memang banyak mulut.

128
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,200
Ayah.

129
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,679
Saya simpan semua duit di sini.

130
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:27,679
Mereka hanya akan tumpukan pada saya.

131
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:29,279
Sebentar lagi, ayah upah sebuah
kereta kuda dan lari dari sini.

132
00:06:30,119 --> 00:06:30,600
Ambil ini.

133
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,399
Tak boleh.

134
00:06:31,799 --> 00:06:32,839
Bagaimana dengan awak jika ayah pergi?

135
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,760
Kita pergi bersama-sama.

136
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:34,559
Ayah.

137
00:06:34,559 --> 00:06:37,000
Kalau nak mati, biar ayah mati dahulu.

138
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:39,000
Ayah akan mengalihkan
perhatian mereka. Awak pergi dahulu.

139
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:41,160
Ayah, saya belum berkahwin.

140
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,239
Saya tak nak mati.

141
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,359
Khabarnya, altar dibina di tepi sungai.

142
00:06:45,559 --> 00:06:47,079
Ayah tunggu saya
di jeti kecil hujung sungai.

143
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,239
Saya akan berpura-pura
jatuh ke dalam sungai.

144
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:50,119
Kemudian, kita berkumpul.

145
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,440
Kita pergi cari pak cik.

146
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,839
Mantera awak dah siap?

147
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,399
Hampir siap.

148
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:59,559
Awak mesti datang.

149
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,600
Percaya pada saya, ayah.

150
00:07:03,119 --> 00:07:03,880
Baik.

151
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,799
Tuan Xue! Tuan Xue! Tuan Xue!

152
00:07:12,359 --> 00:07:13,200
Apa yang terjadi?

153
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,359
Jampi Tiga Panggilan tak pernah gagal.

154
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,760
Takkan...

155
00:07:18,359 --> 00:07:19,519
Tak mungkin.

156
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:25,799
Xue Qianxun. Xue Qianxun.

157
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,279
Xue Qianxun.

158
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:28,799
Boleh tahan.

159
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,559
Sekarang, awak terus panggil nama saya.

160
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,399
Cepat.

161
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,279
Kita tolong Raja Naga
rampas Jampi Seru Hujan.

162
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,320
Ayu sedang cuba menurunkan hujan,

163
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:38,720
habislah dia kalau hujan tak turun.

164
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,600
Cepat.

165
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,040
Awak tak nak tolong Ayu?

166
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,320
Merepek!

167
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,040
Kita akan dijatuhi hukuman petir

168
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,359
jika guna kuasa sihir
untuk ganggu urusan alam manusia.

169
00:07:50,799 --> 00:07:52,559
Raja Naga kuat,
dia boleh tahan disambar petir.

170
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,640
Bagaimana dengan awak?

171
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,760
Awak akan menjadi abu

172
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,160
jika disambar petir.

173
00:07:57,279 --> 00:07:58,200
Namun,

174
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:01,119
saya tak boleh berpeluk tubuh saja.

175
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:04,359
Saya pergi sendiri
jika awak tak nak tolong.

176
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,480
Jangan menyibuk.

177
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:08,880
Ikut saya pulang ke Astaka Luo Feng.

178
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,320
Saya tak nak! Saya...

179
00:08:11,359 --> 00:08:12,440
Xue Qianxun!

180
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,640
Lepaskan saya!

181
00:08:16,359 --> 00:08:17,440
(Astaka Luo Feng)
Penjahat!

182
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,359
Saya nak selamatkan Ayu!

183
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:22,119
Xue Qianxun!

184
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,640
(Menyeru hujan)

185
00:09:00,123 --> 00:09:03,232
(Senyap)

186
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,359
Berpura-pura.

187
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,520
Saya nak tengok awak
boleh berlakon sampai bila.

188
00:09:18,119 --> 00:09:19,119
Mulakan.

189
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,919
Tuan, belum tiba masanya.

190
00:09:27,599 --> 00:09:28,960
Saya nak tengok apa helah awak.

191
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,200
Perhatikan dia.

192
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,359
Jangan biar penipu ini larikan diri.

193
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:34,880
Perlahankan suara,
ini bukan urusan awak.

194
00:09:42,719 --> 00:09:44,599
Berapa lama lagi kita perlu tunggu?

195
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,919
(Rasanya ayah dah larikan diri.)

196
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,520
(Bertahan sebentar lagi.)

197
00:09:51,719 --> 00:09:52,640
Sebatang colok.

198
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,479
Saya perlukan masa sebatang colok.

199
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:55,760
Lamanya.

200
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:58,200
Kalau masa tak tepat,

201
00:09:58,559 --> 00:09:59,880
saya tak dapat turunkan hujan.

202
00:10:00,239 --> 00:10:01,080
Baik.

203
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:04,359
Saya beri awak masa sebatang colok.

204
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:06,559
Namun, saya nak ingatkan awak.

205
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,239
Kalau awak gagal,

206
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,239
ini merupakan kesalahan menipu baginda.

207
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,840
Bakar colok.

208
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:30,520
Kenapa Ayu masih belum sampai?

209
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:33,919
Ayu.

210
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,640
Tuhan.

211
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,679
Tolong berkati Ayu.

212
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,799
Tolong selamatkan anak saya.

213
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,280
Saya bersujud kepada Tuhan.

214
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:06,359
Masa dah tiba, mulakan.

215
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:09,440
Jangan cemas.

216
00:11:09,719 --> 00:11:11,359
Mampukah awak?

217
00:11:11,719 --> 00:11:12,559
Kalau tak boleh,

218
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,880
mengaku saja dan bersujud.

219
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,119
Namun, ini kesalahan menipu baginda,

220
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,719
awak takkan terlepas.

221
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,719
(Tuhan,)

222
00:11:39,599 --> 00:11:40,559
(saya minta maaf )

223
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:42,400
(bagi pihak ayah saya dan diri sendiri.)

224
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:45,640
(Saya tak patut dakwa diri
ialah gadis dewa.)

225
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:48,719
(Namun, sudah lama
Pekan Yuchi dilanda kemarau.)

226
00:11:49,239 --> 00:11:51,440
(Penduduk akan kebuluran
jika keadaan ini berterusan.)

227
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,280
(Saya merayu kepada Tuhan.)

228
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:54,799
(Turunkan hujan.)

229
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,719
Jangan datang sini.

230
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,719
Dewa Hujan Xuan Ming.

231
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:14,200
Pinjam Jampi Seru Hujan kepada saya.

232
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,159
Tak boleh.

233
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:17,039
Saya bersusah payah dapatkan

234
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,599
tugas turunkan hujan
daripada Maharaja Syurga.

235
00:12:19,039 --> 00:12:20,880
Syaitan naga, jangan harap
awak boleh rampasnya.

236
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,080
Saya tak nak guna kekerasan.

237
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,960
Saya cuma nak pinjam sebentar

238
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,719
untuk turunkan hujan di Pekan Yuchi.

239
00:12:26,919 --> 00:12:28,719
Semalam saya dapat
titah daripada Maharaja Syurga

240
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,159
dan turunkan hujan di alam manusia.

241
00:12:30,359 --> 00:12:31,200
Mengarut!

242
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:33,479
Setitik hujan pun
tak turun di Pekan Yuchi.

243
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,200
Saya ialah kura-kura
jika percaya cakap awak.

244
00:12:36,599 --> 00:12:37,760
Cepat halang dia!

245
00:13:38,159 --> 00:13:39,359
Tuan Shen,

246
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:41,479
sudah lama masa berlalu.

247
00:13:41,719 --> 00:13:43,039
Jangankan hujan,

248
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:44,760
awan hitam pun tiada.

249
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,119
Cukup!

250
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:56,280
Tangkap dia!

251
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,159
Ya!

252
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,080
Tangkap dia!

253
00:14:01,599 --> 00:14:03,119
Tangkap penipu itu!

254
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:05,119
Dia ialah penipu.

255
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,919
Kenapa awak tipu kami?

256
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:15,119
Mana Jampi Seru Hujan itu?

257
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:18,640
Berhenti!

258
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:20,719
Tolong saya, Abang Ziyang!

259
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,640
Syaitan naga lagi.

260
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:24,520
Hari itu, awak ganggu
saya bunuh Iblis Darah.

261
00:14:24,919 --> 00:14:27,039
Sekarang awak datang
buli Dewa Hujan pula.

262
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,400
Apa masalahnya?

263
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,719
Awak...

264
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:33,320
Dewa Hujan telah maklumkan
kepada Maharaja Syurga tentang hujan.

265
00:14:33,640 --> 00:14:34,960
Saya juga berada di sana
ketika dia turunkan hujan.

266
00:14:35,599 --> 00:14:37,200
Sudah lama kemarau melanda Pekan Yuchi.

267
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:39,479
Hujan langsung tak turun
di sana baru-baru ini.

268
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:42,359
Saya dah beritahu dia tadi,

269
00:14:42,679 --> 00:14:44,559
saya dah terima rayuan
dari alam manusia

270
00:14:44,719 --> 00:14:46,359
dan turunkan hujan semalam.

271
00:14:46,599 --> 00:14:47,559
Melainkan

272
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:51,320
ada orang memayungi Pekan Yuchi.

273
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:56,520
Pelangi bulat sepatutnya
muncul selepas hujan.

274
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,679
Namun, hujan tak turun pun.

275
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,239
Pekan Yuchi mungkin

276
00:15:02,239 --> 00:15:03,760
telah dihalang oleh sesuatu.

277
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,919
Dihalang?

278
00:15:07,159 --> 00:15:08,200
Kita akan tahu selepas ke sana.

279
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:24,039
Siapa yang ganggu saya seru hujan?

280
00:15:24,599 --> 00:15:26,400
Tunggu sebentar, saya akan cuba lagi.

281
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,320
Awak cuba berapa kali pun sama.

282
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:31,440
Siapa yang hasilkan tirai cahaya

283
00:15:31,599 --> 00:15:32,599
untuk halang hujan?

284
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,479
Kamu masih ingat

285
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,320
Iblis Darah pancarkan
satu cahaya sebelum mati?

286
00:15:38,679 --> 00:15:41,280
Mungkin tirai cahaya ini
ialah kemarahan terakhir dia.

287
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:45,359
Dia mati di Pekan Yuchi.

288
00:15:45,719 --> 00:15:47,599
Dia mahu jadikan
tempat ini kepada tanah terbiar

289
00:15:48,039 --> 00:15:49,080
untuk dikebumikan bersama dia.

290
00:16:07,599 --> 00:16:08,359
Xuan Ming,

291
00:16:08,799 --> 00:16:10,359
sia-sia saja kita buat begini.

292
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:12,080
Kita laporkan kepada Maharaja Syurga.

293
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:13,320
Ya.

294
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:28,119
Pesalah Ruan Ayu,

295
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:30,799
sebarkan khabar angin
dan tipu pegawai atasan.

296
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:32,400
Saya umumkan,

297
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:34,080
dia akan dijatuhi hukuman pancung

298
00:16:34,679 --> 00:16:35,960
sebagai korban kepada Dewa Hujan.

299
00:16:40,479 --> 00:16:43,080
Akhirnya, saya berjaya balas dendam
untuk Abang Zhiyong!

300
00:16:44,119 --> 00:16:44,960
Jangan mengarut!

301
00:16:47,799 --> 00:16:48,840
Ruan Ayu,

302
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:51,559
awak ada pesanan terakhir?

303
00:16:56,239 --> 00:16:57,119
Ada.

304
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:58,919
Saya nak cakap sesuatu.

305
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:00,520
Cakap.

306
00:17:01,719 --> 00:17:02,719
Saya nak mengaku salah.

307
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:06,079
Namun, bukan pada baginda.

308
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:08,839
Saya bersalah

309
00:17:09,560 --> 00:17:10,520
kerana beri harapan

310
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:12,040
kepada penduduk di Pekan Yuchi.

311
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:16,040
Kemudian, mengecewakan kamu pula.

312
00:17:20,839 --> 00:17:23,000
Semua penduduk sekalian,

313
00:17:24,479 --> 00:17:25,439
di sini,

314
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,079
saya minta maaf

315
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,800
daripada kamu semua.

316
00:18:01,359 --> 00:18:02,199
Ayah,

317
00:18:04,319 --> 00:18:05,319
saya bukan anak yang taat.

318
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,359
Saya akan balas budi ayah

319
00:18:14,079 --> 00:18:15,599
di hayat seterusnya.

320
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,520
Wanginya.

321
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:20,920
Mari makan.

322
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:22,719
Makan banyak.

323
00:18:28,959 --> 00:18:29,959
Saya kenal awak!

324
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:32,920
Awak Abang Yuchi yang selamatkan saya!

325
00:18:48,319 --> 00:18:49,439
Abang Yuchi,

326
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,199
kita berjumpa di hayat seterusnya.

327
00:18:58,680 --> 00:18:59,760
Awak dah habis cakap?

328
00:19:04,719 --> 00:19:05,479
Pancung!

329
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,282
(Hukum)

330
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:10,560
Jangan bazirkan kuasa ghaib lagi.

331
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,000
Tirai cahaya Suku Iblis

332
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:17,079
hanya dengar arahan tuannya.

333
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,880
Kita harus mengarah
dengan nama Iblis Darah.

334
00:19:20,479 --> 00:19:21,520
Tiada orang tahu

335
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:23,359
apa gelaran Iblis Darah.

336
00:19:25,123 --> 00:19:26,951
(Gadis Chen Yu, Tuan Yong Sheng)

337
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:30,079
Tuan Yong Sheng.

338
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,599
Awak sedang buat apa?

339
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:11,850
(Pemerintah Abadi)

340
00:20:14,719 --> 00:20:17,560
Pemerintah Abadi,
semua makhluk dengar arahan.

341
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:18,839
Pecahkannya!

342
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:08,160
Hujan dah turun!

343
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:24,599
Berhenti!

344
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,239
Gadis dewa, sila bangun.

345
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:33,160
Maafkan saya kerana biadab.

346
00:21:33,359 --> 00:21:35,239
Tolong maafkan saya.

347
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:36,119
Tak mengapa.

348
00:21:36,359 --> 00:21:37,359
Cepat buka ikatan dia!

349
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:38,400
Ya!

350
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:03,160
Lepaskan saya.

351
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:06,359
Dia penipu, dia bukan gadis dewa!

352
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,280
Dia ialah

353
00:22:07,479 --> 00:22:08,880
syaitan! Dia ialah syaitan!

354
00:22:09,079 --> 00:22:10,640
Tutup mulut perempuan tak waras ini!

355
00:22:14,439 --> 00:22:16,000
Gadis dewa, sila duduk.

356
00:22:16,719 --> 00:22:17,479
Tak perlu.

357
00:22:19,199 --> 00:22:20,000
Liu Yuxiang,

358
00:22:20,439 --> 00:22:22,319
sudah berpuluh tahun awak gelar saya
sebagai pembawa malang.

359
00:22:22,599 --> 00:22:23,760
Awak pasti tak sangka
hari ini akan tiba.

360
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:26,479
Semasa awak suruh Si Botak culik saya,

361
00:22:26,719 --> 00:22:27,880
awak pernah terfikir saat ini?

362
00:22:28,959 --> 00:22:30,920
Bagaimana gadis dewa nak uruskan

363
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:32,000
perempuan tak waras itu?

364
00:22:34,239 --> 00:22:35,239
Biar saya fikir.

365
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,359
Cik Ayu.

366
00:22:38,719 --> 00:22:40,119
Tolonglah, Cik Ayu.

367
00:22:40,319 --> 00:22:40,959
Awak...

368
00:22:41,520 --> 00:22:43,880
Bukan, gadis dewa yang dihormati.

369
00:22:44,119 --> 00:22:45,079
Tolonglah

370
00:22:45,239 --> 00:22:47,160
maafkan anak perempuan saya.

371
00:22:48,319 --> 00:22:49,280
Selama ini,

372
00:22:49,560 --> 00:22:50,439
dia selalu buli penduduk biasa

373
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:51,839
kerana statusnya sebagai

374
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,319
cik muda Keluarga Liu.

375
00:22:53,560 --> 00:22:54,479
Saya dianggap membantu pembuli

376
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,400
jika saya maafkan dia.

377
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:58,560
Betul kata gadis dewa.

378
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:01,640
Penjahat harus dihukum.

379
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:03,239
Pada pendapat saya,

380
00:23:03,599 --> 00:23:05,119
kita patut jatuhkan
hukuman mati ke atas Yuxiang,

381
00:23:05,319 --> 00:23:07,280
kemudian mengarak mayatnya.

382
00:23:07,479 --> 00:23:09,280
Apa pendapat gadis dewa?

383
00:23:09,479 --> 00:23:10,760
Jangan!

384
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:43,640
Dah siap.

385
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:45,239
Untuk 16 hari yang seterusnya,

386
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:46,439
awak harus bersolek sebagai kura-kura

387
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,000
dan berjalan di sekitar pekan ini.

388
00:23:51,319 --> 00:23:52,199
Liu Yuxiang,

389
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:53,959
jika mengejek dan buli orang

390
00:23:54,119 --> 00:23:55,239
ialah hobi awak,

391
00:23:55,439 --> 00:23:56,359
maka awak juga patut

392
00:23:56,479 --> 00:23:57,880
merasai perasaan diejek dan dibuli.

393
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:59,000
Saya harap awak akan berubah

394
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,359
selepas merasai

395
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:01,599
pandangan mengejek orang lain

396
00:24:02,079 --> 00:24:03,160
dan berubah menjadi baik

397
00:24:03,319 --> 00:24:05,319
serta mengasihani orang lain.

398
00:24:07,119 --> 00:24:07,719
Bawa dia pergi.

399
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,640
Ya.

400
00:24:18,959 --> 00:24:21,160
Gadis dewa sangat baik hati.

401
00:24:21,359 --> 00:24:23,119
Saya kagum dengan awak.

402
00:24:23,319 --> 00:24:24,920
Tak perlu, Tuan Shen.

403
00:24:25,319 --> 00:24:26,359
Hari dah lewat.

404
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:28,119
Ayah saya sedang tunggu saya,
saya patut balik rumah.

405
00:24:28,319 --> 00:24:29,199
Gadis dewa,

406
00:24:30,280 --> 00:24:33,199
jangan risau, baginda dah atur semuanya.

407
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,880
Ayah awak telah dibawa ke istana

408
00:24:36,079 --> 00:24:37,520
dan dilayan dengan baik.

409
00:24:37,719 --> 00:24:38,719
Terima kasih kepada baginda.

410
00:24:38,959 --> 00:24:40,199
Terima kasih kepada Tuan Shen juga.

411
00:24:40,439 --> 00:24:42,280
Saya patut buat begini.

412
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:44,920
Bilakah gadis dewa akan masuk ke istana?

413
00:24:45,719 --> 00:24:46,839
Saya juga perlu masuk istana?

414
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:55,439
Terima kasih.

415
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:01,040
Awak ialah Raja Naga Alaf,

416
00:25:01,359 --> 00:25:03,079
tapi berkali-kali cederakan diri

417
00:25:03,280 --> 00:25:04,920
demi seorang gadis biasa.

418
00:25:05,560 --> 00:25:08,000
Berbaloikah awak
berkorban demi cinta ini?

419
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:09,920
Guna sikit penderitaan saya

420
00:25:10,719 --> 00:25:12,160
untuk ditukar dengan kebahagiaan dia,

421
00:25:12,959 --> 00:25:13,760
ia berbaloi.

422
00:25:14,119 --> 00:25:16,640
Nampaknya gadis dewa
tak tahu tentang ini.

423
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,119
Baginda menitahkan

424
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:21,432
(Notis Diraja)
jika gadis dewa berjaya turunkan hujan,

425
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:24,359
dia akan dikurniai emas, sutera
dan pelbagai barang kemas.

426
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,920
(Dilantik sebagai gundik)
Kemudian, dilantik sebagai gundik.

427
00:25:27,119 --> 00:25:28,239
Dilantik sebagai gundik?

428
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:29,239
Betul.

429
00:25:30,319 --> 00:25:33,160
Saya rasa, kita tak patut
biar baginda tunggu lama.

430
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,040
Apa kata kita ke istana sekarang?

431
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:41,199
Tahniah, gadis dewa.

432
00:25:41,959 --> 00:25:44,119
Tahniah, gadis dewa!

433
00:25:47,839 --> 00:25:50,479
Namun, dia akan berkahwin dengan
maharaja dan menjadi gundik.

434
00:25:50,719 --> 00:25:51,920
Awak juga sudi terima hakikat ini?

435
00:25:52,439 --> 00:25:53,560
Begini lebih bagus.

436
00:25:54,040 --> 00:25:55,560
Sebelum ini, tenaga Ayu

437
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:56,959
terjejas kerana saya.

438
00:25:57,359 --> 00:25:58,359
Selepas menjadi gundik,

439
00:25:58,520 --> 00:26:00,760
dia boleh menikmati kemewahan

440
00:26:02,280 --> 00:26:04,000
dan menyerap tenaga dalam istana.

441
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:06,359
Dia akan hidup aman
untuk seumur hidup ini.

442
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,280
Kemudian, meninggal dengan tenang.

443
00:26:09,359 --> 00:26:11,239
Inilah yang saya harap dia dapat.

444
00:26:12,239 --> 00:26:13,359
Maksudnya,

445
00:26:13,800 --> 00:26:15,119
cinta yang bermakna,

446
00:26:15,839 --> 00:26:17,280
adakala sangat indah,

447
00:26:17,800 --> 00:26:20,359
adakala sangat menyedihkan.

448
00:26:35,809 --> 00:26:39,051
(Astaka Luo Feng)

449
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:47,599
Cemas betul saya.

450
00:26:47,959 --> 00:26:50,319
Kenapa Tuan Xue kurung saya di sini?

451
00:26:50,719 --> 00:26:52,800
Bagaimana dengan mereka sekarang?

452
00:27:06,560 --> 00:27:08,479
Awak dah balik, bagaimana dengan Ayu?

453
00:27:14,079 --> 00:27:15,599
Kenapa awak cedera?

454
00:27:18,719 --> 00:27:19,599
Saya tiada apa-apa.

455
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:21,280
Saya akan sembuh
selepas berehat beberapa hari.

456
00:27:21,839 --> 00:27:23,800
Pergi ambil ubat daripada Dewa Nasib.

457
00:27:24,040 --> 00:27:24,760
Ya.

458
00:27:27,439 --> 00:27:29,400
Bagaimana saya nak pergi dengan ini?

459
00:27:38,680 --> 00:27:40,280
Awak ikat Qingqing pada kerusi?

460
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:41,920
Saya buat demi kebaikan dia.

461
00:27:46,719 --> 00:27:49,000
Tentang layanan sama rata
yang awak cakap hari itu,

462
00:27:50,479 --> 00:27:52,199
saya akan cari peluang untuk cubanya.

463
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,079
Awak tercedera lagi?

464
00:28:00,439 --> 00:28:03,040
Luka lama belum pulih,

465
00:28:03,239 --> 00:28:04,640
awak dah tambah luka baharu.

466
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:05,920
Ikut saya.

467
00:28:06,119 --> 00:28:07,119
Biar saya rawat awak.

468
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:21,319
Saya pergi ambil ubat.

469
00:28:21,599 --> 00:28:22,760
Namun, Dewa Nasib

470
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:25,079
berkeras nak datang sini.

471
00:28:26,479 --> 00:28:28,439
Di hadapan perempuan yang kita suka,

472
00:28:28,800 --> 00:28:32,079
kita bukan Raja Naga atau Tuan Xue.

473
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:33,920
Awak patut singkirkan fikiran itu.

474
00:28:34,119 --> 00:28:35,800
Awak harus layan dia

475
00:28:35,959 --> 00:28:37,439
selaku seorang lelaki biasa.

476
00:28:37,599 --> 00:28:38,680
Beri dia layanan sama rata.

477
00:28:45,439 --> 00:28:46,599
Kenapa?

478
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:49,439
Kenapa awak pandang saya begini?

479
00:28:50,959 --> 00:28:53,119
Jangan ingat saya akan maafkan awak

480
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:54,239
jika awak pandang saya begini.

481
00:28:54,359 --> 00:28:56,119
Saya takkan maafkan awak
kerana ikat saya di kerusi.

482
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:58,239
Betulkah awak marah?

483
00:28:58,760 --> 00:29:00,280
Kalau begitu, awak boleh ikat saya.

484
00:29:01,439 --> 00:29:02,680
Tak perlu.

485
00:29:03,959 --> 00:29:07,160
Saya tahu awak buat begitu
demi kebaikan saya.

486
00:29:08,239 --> 00:29:11,000
Namun, awak boleh
bercakap baik-baik dengan saya.

487
00:29:11,359 --> 00:29:12,239
Baik.

488
00:29:13,040 --> 00:29:14,199
Awak nak minum teh?

489
00:29:15,199 --> 00:29:17,479
